Structure of program this structure itself created by netbeans ide 
  web pages (here create all jsp and html file)
  remote file 
  Source Packages (here create all action classes)
  Test Packages
  Libraries (here add all the required jar files ex : jdbc connector, server etc)
  Tesst Libraries
  Configurations files
  
  
  Also make a folder for all the images.
  
   *** web.xml must be present under web page unde WEB-INF folder
   *** in web.xml we have to do all the mapping of the servlet.
